  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2022-03-30",
    "date": "2023-08-10T12:41:12Z",
    "text": "Energy Permitting Certainty Act\n\nThis bill requires the Department of the Interior to process applications for permits to drill under a valid oil or gas lease even if there are any pending civil actions, provided that the civil actions do not directly affect or involve the application or underlying lease."
  },
